{
  "texts": [
    "These chatbots, like ChatGPT, can generate human-like text based on vast amounts of data (Briganti, 2024).",
    "Additionally, they can understand and respond to a broader array of queries more accurately by using machine learning algorithms (Khennouche et al., 2024).",
    "These features enforce the idea of integrating LLM-based chatbots into programming education as a potential learning tool (Adeshola & Adepoju, 2023; Haindl & Weinberger, 2024; Kasneci et al., 2023; Sun et al., 2024).",
    "For instance, ChatGPT can explain complex concepts, provide code snippets, debug errors, and offer recommendations for best practices.",
    "Its ability to engage in dynamic and context-aware conversations can make it a valuable tool for both novice and advanced learners (Speth et al., 2023)."
  ]
}